---
import MainHead from '../components/MainHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
const yearsOfExp = new Date().getFullYear() - 2019;

---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<MainHead
			title="Patrick Moreno"
			description="What's Patrick been up to ðŸ¤”"
		/>
		<style>
			.heroImg {
				max-height: 24rem;
				object-fit: cover;
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			.heroImg img {
				width: 100%;
			}

			.bio {
				font-size: var(--f-u1);
				line-height: 2;
				margin-top: 4em;
			}

			.wrapper.bio {
				max-width: 50em;
			}
			.heading-about {
				margin-left: 2rem;
			}
			.skills-table {
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: space-between;
				width: 100%;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}
			.skills-second-col {
				width: 60%
			}
			.about-header-3 {
				margin-bottom: .25rem 0 !important;
			}
			.work-exp-date {
				line-height: 0;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Nav />
		<div class="wrapper">
			<h1 class="heading-about">About Me</h1>
			<div class="bio wrapper">
				<p>
					I started my journey quite early attempting to understand big books on HTML from the library in elementary. In highschool I was manipulating webpages and graphics on social sites for friends and myself. After trying out some Java and C++ courses in my under grad I changed my studies over to software engineering. Completed a diploma in Digital Design & Development from British Columbia Institute of Technology with distinction. Now I am out getting field tested and blazing my way through the jungle that is tech!
				</p>

					<!-- <input type="text" placeholder="Search Skills"/> -->
				<h2>Skills</h2>
				<div class="skills-table">
					<h3>Proficient</h3>
					<div class="skills-second-col">
						HTML5, CSS3, Javascript ES6+, Vue, Nodejs, Express, Git, REST, JSON, CouchDB (NoSQL), PouchDB, Linux, PM2, Slack
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="skills-table">
					<h3>Experienced</h3>
					<div class="skills-second-col">
						Electron, React, AWS(S3), Bootstrap, Illustrator, Photoshop, UI/UX Design, PuTTY, SSH, SSL, Wordpress, Postman, Nodemailer, Trello, Digital Ocean
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="skills-table">
					<h3>Knowledgable</h3>
					<div class="skills-second-col">
						Bash & Batch scripting, Cron, MongoDB, Figma, Invision, Laravel, PHP, Cypress, Jest, Nginx, MySQL, Stripe 
					</div>
				</div>

				<h2>Work Experience - {yearsOfExp} years</h2>	
				<div class="skills-table">
					<div>
						<h3 class="about-header-3">TMMedia</h3>
						<div class="work-exp-date">2019 - Present</div>
					</div>
					<div class="skills-second-col">
						<li>
							Developing and maintaining dance competition registration and management web application using Vue, Nodejs and CouchDB
						</li>
						<li>
							Improving internal tools for video, photo production using Laravel, Vue and Electron
						</li>
						<li>
							Monitor, and fix issues with servers serving company websites, and web apps, using systemctl, nginx, PM2 and other utilities
						</li>
						<li>
							Developed kiosk software and TV slideshow web app using Electron and PHP
						</li>
						<li>
							Interviewd, and guided design intern
						</li>
						<li>
							Design low and high fidelity mockups using, Illustrator and Figma
						</li>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="skills-table">
					<div>
						<h3 class="about-header-3">BCPVA</h3>
						<div class="work-exp-date">2019 (2 Months)</div>
					</div>
					<div class="skills-second-col">
						<li>
							Designed mockups of new website with Illustrator
						</li>
						<li>
							Created sitemap, styleguides, iconography and documentation
						</li>
						<li>
							Developed website with wordpress using custom functions and CSS
						</li>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="skills-table">
					<div>
						<h3 class="about-header-3">ACL/Galvanize</h3>
						<div class="work-exp-date">2019 (2 Months)</div>
					</div>
					<div class="skills-second-col">
						<li>
							Tested components with Jest/React Testing Library and Cypress.io
						</li>
						<li>
							Assited with component migration to a new UI Library
						</li>
						<li>
							Documented react components
						</li>
						<li>
							Collaborated with designers to setup new tokens
						</li>
						<li>
							Created tickets with Jira
						</li>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
